description:
C-shaped, glass hotel in artsy Montparnasse

Modernity in Montparnasse
You'll find sophisticated, modern lodgings at the curved, 4-star Hotel Catalogne Paris Gare Montparnasse, built in 2004. Gare Montparnasse is around the corner for easy train and metro access. For the macabre among you, the catacombs are 1 km away.

La vie bohme
The artsy Montparnasse (once Picasso and Hemingway's stomping grounds) is packed with brasseries, jazz clubs, and cinemas. For a cool view, you can head to the other side of Gare Montparnasse, where elevators whizz you up to the 56th-floor viewing lounge of Tour Montparnasse.

Secret garden
Guests appreciate the hotel's choice of breakfasts a full hot feast or a simpler, continental option. You can meet friends and colleagues for lunch and dinner in the modern restaurant and cocktail bar, which spills over in summer to an intimate courtyard garden.

Curved bedrooms
The curved facade creates unusual perspectives in the clean, compact guestrooms. A few have glimpses of the Eiffel Tower, while others overlook the internal courtyard garden. Free WiFi is available in all rooms.

HOTEL_AMENITY.value: Wireless Internet access is complimentary throughout the Hotel Catalogne Paris Gare Montparnasse. A computer station with DVD/CD player, printer, scanner, and high-speed Internet access is available on a first-come, first-served basis. A private, secure parking garage accommodates 70 vehicles (surcharge). The hotel is located near a metro station.

DINING.value:
Restaurant 40 - The restaurant features a menu that combines classic French cuisine with original creations, and also offers a carefully selected buffet. Located on the ground floor, 40 is a bright, airy, and spacious restaurant with windows that overlook the Catalogne Square and the internal courtyard gardens. Wooden floors and hints of color on the walls create modern contemporary surroundings in which to enjoy breakfast, lunch, or dinner.

Weng Bar - Dark wood furniture and warm tones of red and purple create an intimate and cozy atmosphere at Le Weng Bar. The setting is a perfect meeting place whatever the time of day, and the bar also offers complimentary newspapers and free WiFi access. Continental breakfast is served in the morning. The Restaurant Menu is also available at the Bar.

RECREATION.value:
One block from the hotel, the elevated Jardin Atlantique, atop the Montparnasse Station, has running paths and a playground. An outdoor ice rink at the foot of the Montparnasse Tower 2 blocks away is open in winter. The AquaBoulevard theme park, 10 minutes from the hotel by Metro, includes a water park, fitness club, swimming pool, tennis and squash courts, and helicopter pad. Bicycle rentals are also available nearby.

The recreational activities listed below are available either on site or near the hotel; fees may apply.

GOLD.value: The reasonably priced Htel Concorde Montparnasse offers comfortable, modern rooms and outdoor dining in artsy Montparnasse. You'll find Gare Montparnasse around the corner, giving easy access to the metro and trains. With 354 guestrooms, and multiple conference rooms, the hotel is a solid spot for business travelers. All rooms offer free WiFi.

GUESTS_LOVE.value:
Guests Love
  • Clean, comfortable rooms

  • Free WiFi in all guestrooms

  • Great location, close to Gare Montparnasse and Gat Metro Station

  • Entirely non-smoking

    • Keep in Mind
  • Non-opening windows on the street side

  • Rooms can be quite warm

END_OF_THE_DAY.value:
At the end of the day
Our guests appreciate the modern style and efficient service at Htel Concorde Montparnasse. Some guests mention unpredictable air conditioning, but most rave about the cleanliness of the guestrooms.

ROOM_FEATURE.value: At Hotel Catalogne Paris Gare Montparnasse, you'll be just a 5-minute drive from Tour Montparnasse and Cartier Foundation for Contemporary Art. The bar is a great place to grab a drink, and guests looking for a bite to eat can check out Restaurant 040, which serves French cuisine and is open for breakfast, lunch, and dinner. Rooms at this upscale hotel offer up nice touches like premium bedding and designer toiletries, along with 24-hour room service and LCD TVs.
